  "body": "<p>Hi !!! <a href=\"http://olennka-handmade.blogspot.com/\">Olennka</a> here! When I saw Amy's STITCHED collection I fell in love at the first sight. I love all the items from this line. Especialy I adore simple brown papers which can be used as the base of the Layout. They can easily replace white cardstocks which I use as the base because they are very neutral.</p><p>To create my LO I used Heartfelt paper as the base and Thrifted paper which I cut for the pieces. Then I stuck the scraps to the base . I stopped in the middle of the base, because I wanted to leave some free space. </p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/e9d167ffe8b7db56.jpg?v=1782525728\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Then I sew along every paper scrap and applied gesso on the center of the Layout. I like to do this because it exposes the main place of my Layout, also I often use watercolors and gesso is the best to prime the paper. At the center I placed piece of paper for journaling . In this case I chose \"curious\" because it reminds me Curious George which is my son's favorite cartoon. Also it was inspiration for my title, I wanted to weave this word to the rest of the title. </p><p>I added photo of my child, with tag under it and I wrote the title. I wrote it with brush and black ink, I wanted to look like a child wrote it :)</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/d0ee6d8a147155da.jpg?v=1782525731\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/80335e4895e2d1fa.jpg?v=1782525733\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Then I added some stickers in the free are and I had to add the NOTES epoxy sticker because it's so cute . At the end just few ink splashes and voila, done ! I hope you like it as much as I do :)</p><p><em>How lovely! Thanks for sharing, </em><a href=\"http://olennka-handmade.blogspot.com/\"><em>Olennka</em></a><em>! Other Design Team member posts can be found </em><em>here</em><em>. Shop for Amy Tangerine products at your local scrapbook stores and online at </em><a href=\"http://www.shareasale.com/r.cfm?u=530666&amp;b=199868&amp;m=24698&amp;afftrack=simon%20home%20page&amp;urllink=www%2Esimonsaysstamp%2Ecom\"><em>Simon Says Stamp</em></a><em> and </em><a href=\"http://www.shareasale.com/r.cfm?u=530666&amp;b=213361&amp;m=25838&amp;afftrack=Amy%20tangerine&amp;urllink=www%2Ebluemoonscrapbooking%2Ecom%2FCategoryProductList%2Ejsp%3Fcat%3DShop%253AManufacturers%253AAmerican%2BCrafts%3AAmerican%2BCrafts%2BAmy%2BTangerine\"><em>Blue Moon Scrapbooking</em></a><em> and </em><a href=\"http://www.shareasale.com/r.cfm?u=530666&amp;b=33086&amp;m=7429&amp;afftrack=&amp;urllink=store%2Escrapbook%2Ecom%2Fproducts%2F%3Fw%3Damy%2Btangerine\"><em>Scrapbook.com</em></a><em>. </em></p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>"
